I'm uploading this video of the discovery of Noah's ark on mt. Ararat. The discovery was made in the 80's, so this is a transfer from old VHS to PAL DVD. Just (double?) click on the finished download, and it will mount and burn on DVD through what ever program you've got assigned for this. You don't even have to remove it from the download folder, and that's nice, because then you are helping others to get this video too.. 
:-)
Ron Wyatt, who made the discovery, is unfortunately dead. Cancer took him away to Jesus in 1999, but this is far from being the only important discovery this man made to prove the accuracy and reliability of the Bible. Seek and you shall find..

The narrator is Norwegian, so I'm only writing the above for those that live in other countries, but have friends that are Scandinavian, or maybe you've forgotten the language..? :-)

